{"type": "article", "id": 21690, "title": "Nebula & Why Knot Table by Kino Guerin", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-02T07:34:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185104KzgAjOHn3hpovyUE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">加拿大设计师喜欢将木板弯曲来设计桌子，这张 Nebula（星云）桌使用了核桃木，木条下面绕了两圈，像是打了一个结。咖啡桌 Why Knot 也将缠绕的木结作为桌腿，带有华丽的雕塑感。书桌 Salto 则只将一根木腿缠绕一圈，其余三根是直立的，它们之间构成更强的对比，颠覆了传统的造型，也给空间带来一丝趣味。有兴趣可以查看他的工作室。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185102BDJGwhgb2kiW0l3x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42565947\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071851038bLGcjheqCVMzNWt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185103ywvaLgTH1FB2DnGM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185104NLlsJwu2QHkG0hZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}